name: Alice Nakiri (Food Wars) LoRA
description:
3. Food Wars model. 🍣

Alice Nakiri LoRA.

Using short hair and red eyes as prompt can help.

Can work well with a weight around 0.5-1. Best if you try around yourself.

Got some really nice results with MeinaMix.
But it works great on other models too. Would love reviews and see what can be generated with this.

NSFW works pretty well too.
